snippet.title: Amber Heard Loses Key Witness That Once Came To Her Defense
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Loses Key Witness That Once Came To Her Defense
Subscribe To InformOverload: http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA

Amber Heard’s close friend Amanda De Cadenet says that she has changed her mind about amber heard and will not be coming to her defense. She says that after she heard the audio tapes of amber heard and johnny depp fighting,  she says she feels misled. This is a huge blow to amber heard because Amanda De Cadenet is a well known metoo activist, as well as a womens right activist, and she was supposed to testify against johnny depp.
